casebody.data:
First Department,

August, 1978

(August 3, 1978) Pan American World Airways, Inc., v Etsia, Inc., et al. (And a Third-Party Action.)

—Motion to dismiss appeal denied. The appeal is deemed to be taken from the judgment entered on March 23, 1978 and the notice of appeal deemed corrected accordingly. (See National Bank of North Amer. v Kory, 63 AD2d 579.) Concur—Murphy, P. J., Silverman, Evans, Lane and Markewich, JJ.
